raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Player: Hey
Player: Online at this time?
Caleb: Hey!
Caleb: Yeah I'm just trying to finish up some of Naomi's work while she's asleep lol
Caleb: img: caleb/6
Caleb: Don't tell her! 🤫😇
Player: You should take a break too
Player: It's late
Caleb: She'll be able to sleep earlier if some of this is out of the way 😅
Player: But then you'll be tired tomorrow
Caleb: Checkmate I guess
if Story.has_flag(\"Naomi1\"):
	Caleb: Knowing Naomi is less stressed makes me less stressed
	Caleb: Just look at her 😇
	Caleb: img: naomi/24
	Caleb: Okay maybe not right now.. 🤨
	Caleb: She's mumbling weird stuff again 😂
	Player: Cute but scary 😂
Player: Thanks for helping Mabel today by the way!
Caleb: Oh anytime
Caleb: She seemed a little distressed at first but she was definitely more relaxed by the end
Player: Dw, she's always stressed about something 😄
Player: Wanna see how cute and nervous she was before the shoot?
Caleb: Sure thing!
- [Show a little]
	Player: Here's a little tease then
	Player: img: mabel/150
- [Show a lot]
	Player: Here's the one I like
	Player: img: mabel/115
Caleb: Oh wow..
Player: I know right? 😉
Caleb: You're a lucky guy ☺️
Player: You're the one who got to spend the whole evening with her haha
Caleb: Ah true! But you know it's not the same haha
Caleb: I don't see things like that while I'm working 🙂
- Well maybe you should
	Player: Well maybe you should
- And if I say you can?
	Player: And if I say you can?
Caleb: Then I'd have a difficult time focusing 😂
Caleb: Especially with someone like Mabel
Player: Seriously though 😆
Player: Is she your type?
Caleb: Oh you really mean it that way 😀
Caleb: I thought I was imagining things at this time of night lol
Player: You're not 😌
Caleb: She reminds me a lot of a girl I used to really like
Caleb: So I kinda do think she's my type haha 😅
Player: That's cute
Caleb: What's on your mind though?
Player: She might have a crush on you.. just checking if the feeling is mutual
Caleb: Awh seriously? That's making me blush haha
Caleb: She really is sweet
Caleb: Is that something you mind?
- Not at all
	Player: Not at all
- Trying to ignite the spark here!
	Player: Trying to ignite the spark here!
Caleb: Wow, you and Naomi are both so forward haha
Caleb: In a good way
Caleb: Me and Mabel huh
Caleb: Actually Naomi has seen other guys while we date
Player: Wow really?
Caleb: Yeah for sure
Caleb: She's quite popular in some circles 
Caleb: But she's also been having trouble finding someone
Player: Really? Why?
Caleb: She's picky and doesn't like jerks and there's a lot them around
Caleb: Always asks my opinion and permission
- Wow, you guys are tight [if Story.has_flag(\"Naomi1\")]
	Player: Wow you guys are tight!
	Caleb: We are...
	Caleb: And lately she's been asking about you haha
	Player: Whoa.. really?
	Caleb: No spoilers... buuut you have nothing to worry about from me 😁
	Player: Wow seriously? Haha
- I wish Mabel and I had that
	Player: I wish Mabel and I had that
	Caleb: I think you guys look great from my point of view
	Player: Do we?
Caleb: Mhmm
Caleb: Naomi even tried to find a girl for me 😅
Caleb: I told her I was happy with the simple things
Caleb: Actually, I hope she's not the one that put you up to this 😂
Player: I didn't even know!
Player: But now I have someone to scheme with
Caleb: Awwh jeez 😆
Caleb: Oh wow look at the time..
Caleb: I'll call in for the night or else I won't make it to class tomorrow
Caleb: Don't scheme too hard friend
Player: No promises!
Player: Night!
Caleb: Night!
=> END"
